arts.ttl: PLAYER RATINGS: How Carlisle United fared against Harrogate Town
arts.sum: Carlisle United drew 1-1 at home with Harrogate Town – so how did we rate the players at Brunton Park?

arts.ttl: Carlisle United expect defender to need surgery
arts.sum: Archie Davies could be set for a lengthy lay-off with Carlisle United expecting the wing-back to need shoulder surgery.

arts.ttl: Armstrong goal earns Carlisle United a point against Harrogate
arts.sum: REPORT: Luke Armstrong's goal against his former club earned Carlisle United a point in front of 8,297 fans at Brunton Park.

arts.ttl: Luke Armstrong scores against former club as Harrogate rescue point at Carlisle
Carlisle United sign former Championship forward
arts.sum: Carlisle United have gone into the free agent market to sign former Millwall forward Tyler Burey on a short-term deal.

arts.ttl: Time for leaders in tough times, says Carlisle United boss
arts.sum: Mike Williamson says “leaders” must emerge from Carlisle United’s struggles as the Blues aim to get off the bottom of League Two today.

arts.ttl: Carlisle United learn first round opponents in FA Youth Cup
arts.sum: Carlisle United have been handed an away tie against non-league opposition in the first round of this season's FA Youth Cup.

arts.ttl: Harrogate boss has his say on Carlisle United and Williamson
arts.sum: Harrogate Town manager Simon Weaver expects to encounter a Carlisle United side who are “well up for it” this weekend.

arts.ttl: Carlisle United teenager makes loan move to Workington Reds
arts.sum: Teenage Carlisle United prospect Sam Hetherington has joined Workington Reds on loan until the end of the year.

arts.ttl: Carlisle United fans plan tribute to Jay Cartmell
arts.sum: Carlisle United fans are being encouraged to join in a tribute to eight-year-old Jay Cartmell at this weekend's game against Harrogate Town.
